BigShots Vero Beach
BigShots Golf is a state-of-the-art golf recreation and entertainment facility powered by BigShots proprietary golf technology.
Situated on 10 acres, BigShots Golf in Vero Beach is a two-story family entertainment experience that offers a full-service restaurant, 2 bars, a private event space and a 30 tee-box climate controlled experience.
Business Hours
Monday – Thursday: 10am – 10pm
Friday: 10am – 11pm
Saturday: 9am – 12am
Sunday: 9am – 10pm
Contact
3456 US HWY 1, Vero Beach, Florida 32960
772-979-GOLF (4653)
